### Keyboard shortcut
# CTRL+CMD+left : Desktop left
# CTRL+CMD+Right: Desktop right
# CTRL+CMD+Up   : Mission Control
# CTRL+CMD+Down : App Expose
### Mouse Shortcut
# Gesture+Left  : Desktop left  (as keyboard input)
# Gesture+Right : Desktop right (as keyboard input)
# Gesture+Up    : Mission Control
# Gesture+Down  : App Expose
# ScrollLeft    : Forward
# ScrollRight   : Back
